21:39.970 --> 21:40.780
[Padam]

21:40.810 --> 21:41.700
[Padam Sekarang]

21:41.730 --> 21:42.990
[Cikgu Lin suruh kita pergi
ke Kelas Tuisyen Yuan hujung minggu]

21:43.020 --> 21:43.760
[Padam]

21:43.780 --> 21:44.430
