37:07.960 --> 37:09.670
Ketua pasukan.

37:10.190 --> 37:11.390
1 lawan 0.

37:11.630 --> 37:13.490
Kamu pun taklah hebat sangat.

37:15.480 --> 37:16.630
Bagus, kawan-kawan!

37:16.630 --> 37:17.320
Teruskan begini!

37:17.320 --> 37:17.800
Teruskan begini!

37:17.800 --> 37:19.030
Marilah.

